481200,"uid":136639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T03:14:32.000Z","msg":"可能係你女友太蠢"},{"pid":"179f8932c70376c8506c9b2360d1ea195170897b","tid":481200,"uid":130466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T03:17:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>由細到大父母都好少係身邊<br />\n結果好細個就乜都識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到而家拍拖成日覺得自己一個仲好<br />\n根本就唔洗女朋友<br />\n有無人有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有女朋友=湊多個</blockquote><br />\n 咁巴打應該要考慮下我， 我都好獨立。 <br />\n<br />\n同我拍拖會宅係同一空間然後各有各做自己野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5deb7767b281e2011d16f217d6c8b87ad6ca8a","tid":481200,"uid":68278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T03:18:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>由細到大父母都好少係身邊<br />\n結果好細個就乜都識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到而家拍拖成日覺得自己一個仲好<br />\n根本就唔洗女朋友<br />\n有無人有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有女朋友=湊多個</blockquote><br />\n呢個真 又要兼顧埋佢啲野<br />\n仲要久唔久發下脾氣<br />\n有時都真係覺得幾煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ff422a05a73543c16a6973ea20d13ff6d875ad","tid":481200,"uid":68278,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T03:20:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時仲覺得自己一個人做起野上黎高效率啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開始覺得同人溝通嘥時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我其實一直都覺得係<br />\n一個人做野又爽手 想幾時訓就幾時訓<br />\n係啲人成日笑我無拖拍我先去溝女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對上一個都仲未忘記到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb88bb961ff99777b23a94a9bef77aa243aca28","tid":481200,"uid":68278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T03:21:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能係你女友太蠢</blockquote><br />\n我都覺得係<br />\n由其是發嬲果陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e35d31bfd5a614e2a2ffe155c61643be89b9efda","tid":481200,"uid":159448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T03:22:02.000Z","msg":"我都想搵個女強人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce00e9fb378a58e3594dc59713229df0aa6ba845","tid":481200,"uid":68278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T03:25:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想搵個女強人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打試過奶野？"},{"pid":"d5a2ff0749bcee85a8e0f7be3a28639acc9a4508","tid":481200,"uid":37144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T03:26:17.000Z","msg":"兩睇啦 一個人始終有佢強 有佢弱既時候<br />\n強緊既時侯自己做哂緊係冇所謂 但弱既時候有個人係身邊都唔係壞事黎<br />\n你只要唔好搵個太痂身同唔好比好多麻煩你既其實已經好好<br />\n同有時有段穩定關系唔會咁易亂諗野 其實仲易專心做野"},{"pid":"08c26432fb78578cc4d69c9326d2451543a6d039","tid":481200,"uid":68278,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T03:31:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩睇啦 一個人始終有佢強 有佢弱既時候<br />\n強緊既時侯自己做哂緊係冇所謂 但弱既時候有個人係身邊都唔係壞事黎<br />\n你只要唔好搵個太痂身同唔好比好多麻煩你既其實已經好好<br />\n同有時有段穩定關系唔會咁易亂諗野 其實仲易專心做野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人太獨立 弱既時候根本都可以自己搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算同女朋友講佢都唔會幫到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae2299535a44148d2e4e2f1bb44fdd6c6e5d6b4","tid":481200,"uid":149137,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T03:41:43.000Z","msg":"唉屌 心聲"},{"pid":"a7a66b0426cfd28864a79b110be9fa7e7970ecb8","tid":481200,"uid":74262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T03:43:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68df35ae8212ae107063c77c5385e73d99d20e53","tid":481200,"uid":67225,"li